\"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1018, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.998457036642127, \"rank\": 0.0008418339418388901, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Parisian newspaper\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"anthem\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"the measures\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"its invasion\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Interior Minister Gerald Darmanin criticised Portes' comments as having \\\"hints of anti-Semitism,\\\" while Yonathan Arfi, head of the Crif Jewish organisation, accused him of \\\"putting a target on the backs\\\" of Israeli athletes.\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9536817650793806, \"rank\": 0.04308553689245888, \"text\": \"Interior Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Hungary\"}, {\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"score\": 0.9999492342038684, \"rank\": 4.56858774444209e-05, \"text\": \"Gerald\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\"}, {\"begin\": 1173, \"end\": 1179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.9993417463964072, \"rank\": 0.0006530555623630258, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resou